import React from 'react';
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Switch,
  Route
} from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Budget,
  Inventory,
  Reports,
  Recipes,
  Orders,
  Goals,
  Dashboard,
  Settings
} from './pages';
import { Grid } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import 'semantic-ui-css/semantic.min.css';

class App extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Grid>
         <Router>
        
          <Switch>
            <Route exact path='/'>
              <Dashboard />
            </Route>
            <Route path='/inventory'>
              <Inventory />
            </Route>
            <Route path='/budget'>
              <Budget />
            </Route>
            <Route path='/goals'>
              <Goals />
            </Route>
            <Route path='/settings'>
              <Settings />
            </Route>
            <Route path='/reports'>
              <Reports />
            </Route>
            <Route path='/recipes'>
              <Recipes />
            </Route>
            <Route path='/orders'>
              <Orders />
            </Route>
          </Switch>
        </Router>
      </Grid>
     
    )
  }
}
export default App;
